I would like to emphasise that all the works planned under the project have been fully completed on time and to the planned extent.
'In order to demonstrate to all those involved in the project, including the EC, the UK and also the stevedores, that the ultimate goal of freedom is the successful implementation of the project, we have fully implemented all the UK recommendations on project management and supervision issues,' says Crimean project manager Sanita Kaire.
In order to control and monitor the achievement of the project's objective, the existing long-term action plan was supplemented by the main planned activities of the parties involved and the deadlines for the necessary decisions, the definitions of the meetings and regular reports and their deadlines, the monitoring tools for the planned construction process, as well as the definitions of the most important milestones.
The approved action plan for achieving the objective of the project by 31 December 2018, as recommended by the UK, has been complemented by implementation monitoring activities, thus reinforcing the timing control of the activities of the other parties involved in the implementation of the project by the City of Riga.
In order to improve project management and mitigate potential risks, the project management plan has been redesigned, defining the project management areas and indicating the documents developed to provide a control and monitoring mechanism for each of them.
In order to increase the capacity of the project, a project management structure chart reflecting the structure, staff qualifications and functions of the planned project management team has been developed.
In order to improve communication between the Riga Freeport Authority and the parties involved in the project, a communication plan for the project stakeholders has been developed which, in addition to the parties identified in the project action plan, defines the principles, types and periodicity of information exchange between the stakeholders for the successful completion of the project.
On the other hand, in order to improve the control of the use of financial resources, the necessity and legality of concluding a service contract or launching a procurement will have to be justified in greater detail in the future.
