"Choosing the right combination of foods is very important to achieve the desired weight loss results", says Laura Romeraite-Kuklieriene, a registered dietitian in Lithuania.
And it's easy to do in the summertime when we have fresh fruit, berries, and vegetables in our gardens.
A balanced combination of foods can help you not only to lose weight but also to stimulate various bodily processes.
Pasta and vinegar are a winning combination because they provide a long-lasting buzz and help fight fat.
Studies published in the European Journal of Clinical Nutrition have shown that vinegar has a beneficial effect on blood glucose levels and can make us feel more alert.
Cayenne pepper and a protein-rich meal, such as poultry or a protein shake, not only make you feel more at home but also reduce cravings for large meals on subsequent meals.
